OL,3,CDad, 32, died from organ failure after
OL,4,Cgetting tattoo in garden shed - inquest
OL,6,FA dad-of-two died from organ failure
OL,7,Fafter getting a tattoo in a garden
OL,8,Fshed, an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FBen Larry contracted a serious
OL,11,Finfection following the ink work in
OL,12,Fthe week leading to his death on 6 May
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FAn inquest into the 32-year-old's
OL,16,Fdeath at Teesside Coroner's Court
OL,17,Fheard the dad's leg became infected
OL,18,Fafter receiving a tattoo.
