OL,3,CDad, 32, died from organ failure after
OL,4,Cgetting tattoo in garden shed - inquest
OL,6,FAssistant coroner Paul Appleton
OL,7,Fconcluded that Mr Larry, from Ormesby,
OL,8,Fon Teesside, died as a result of a
OL,9,Fmulti-organ failure caused by an
OL,10,Finfection in his right leg.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the inquest on Thursday
OL,13,F(11 April), Mr Appleton said: "This
OL,14,Finfection was secondary to tattoo work
OL,15,Fthat Benjamin had done to his right
OL,16,Fleg on 1 May 2023.
OL,18,F"That tattoo work was performed at
OL,19,Funregistered premises."
