OL,6,FA 35-year-old man had previously been
OL,7,Farrested in connection with the
OL,8,Fincident but the case was dropped by
OL,9,FCleveland Police due to "evidential
OL,10,Fdifficulties".
OL,12,FDespite the criminal case being
OL,13,Fdropped, Middlesbrough Council
OL,14,Flaunched a civil case against
OL,15,Ftattooist Tony James Learmount.
OL,17,FHe was found guilty of operating in a
OL,18,Fgarden shed not registered to carry
OL,19,Fout tattooing at Teesside Magistrates'
OL,20,FCourt in January.
