OL,6,FProsecutor Thomas Durance said on 9
OL,7,FMay 2023, public protection officers
OL,8,Ffrom Middlesbrough Council were
OL,9,Fcontacted by Cleveland Police
OL,10,Ffollowing the death of a man from
OL,11,Fsepsis.
OL,13,FMr Durance told the court: "The
OL,14,Finfection had originally developed
OL,15,Faround the area of a new tattoo.
