OL,6,F"Cleveland Police investigated and
OL,7,Fthis led to confirmation of the
OL,8,Ftattooist being Mr Tony James
OL,9,FLearmount, of Donington Green,
OL,10,FMiddlesbrough - the same location
OL,11,Fwhere the tattoo had taken place."
OL,13,FThe council's case was proven in
OL,14,FLearmount's absence and magistrates
OL,15,Ffined the tattooist #1,000 and ordered
OL,16,Fhim to pay a #400 victim surcharge and
OL,17,F#300 towards the council costs.
