OL,6,FCleveland Police previously issued a
OL,7,Fwarning to the public of the dangers
OL,8,Fof unlicensed tattooists, urging
OL,9,Fpeople to check the Body Art register
OL,10,Fbefore visiting a tattoo parlour.
OL,12,FFollowing Mr Larry's death, his
OL,13,Fparents said: "Our precious, adored,
OL,14,Fkind and caring son was loved by
OL,15,Feveryone. He touched so many hearts.
OL,17,F"No parent should lose a child, no
OL,18,Fchild should lose their daddy and no
OL,19,Fgrandparent should lose a grandchild.
